import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <header>
           <Navbar bg="dark" variant='dark' expand="lg" collapseOnSelect>
    <Container>       
  <Navbar.Brand href="/">Vivokal</Navbar.Brand>
   </Container>
     <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav className="ml-auto">
         <NavDropdown title="Categories" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
           <NavDropdown.Item href="/sellers">Sellers</NavDropdown.Item>
           <NavDropdown.Item href="/helpers">Local Help-Men</NavDropdown.Item>
           <NavDropdown.Item href="/food">Famous Food</NavDropdown.Item>
           <NavDropdown.Divider />
           <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Close</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>
      <Nav.Link href="/Products">Products</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="/cart">Cart</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="/login">Sign In</Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link href="/feedback">Feedback</Nav.Link>
       </Nav>   
      </Navbar.Collapse>
   
  </Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Header
